  "instructions": [
    "1. Dissolve the kanten in water and bring to a boil. Reduce heat and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "2. Add diced tomatoes, cumin, chili powder, and salt to the kanten mixture. Simmer for an additional 10 minutes.",
    "3. Warm tortillas by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20-30 seconds.",
    "4. Assemble tacos by spooning the kanten mixture onto a tortilla, followed by shredded lettuce, diced avocado, and a dollop of vegan sour cream.",
    "5. Serve immediately and top with salsa.",
    "6. Serve hot."
